data.description: Experience the best of island living from this charming bungalow-style home on a shy 1/2 acre in a quaint waterfront neighborhood on Vashon Island. Instantly greeted with breathtaking views & warm ambiance of the arched entry, this 1911 home offers the timeless allure of historic charm & modern comforts. With 3 beds, 2 baths & an updated interior, this one level home overlooking marinas offers a front-row seat to the maritime activites & fireworks that grace the Harbor. Iconic Mt. Rainier views from the spacious living, dining & primary bedroom ensuite are always a treat. Conveniently located near town, ferries & buses while nearby beaches, hiking & the amenities of the Burton Coffee Stand & the Burton Adventure Center are down the street.
